        public PCSHealthMonitorReport(Date generationDate,
                              PCSDaemonStatus fmStatus,
                              PCSDaemonStatus wmStatus,
                              PCSDaemonStatus rmStatus,
                              List batchStubStatus,
                              List crawlerStatus,
                              List latestProductsIngested,
                              List jobHealthStatus,
                              List crawlerHealthStatus)
        Constructs a new PCSHealthMonitorReport with the given parameters.
        Parameters:
        generationDate - The Date that this report was generated.
        fmStatus - The PCSDaemonStatus for the File Manager.
        wmStatus - The PCSDaemonStatus for the Workflow Manager.
        rmStatus - THe PCSDaemonStatus for the Resource Manager.
        batchStubStatus - A of PCSDaemonStatuses for each XmlRpcBatchStub.
        crawlerStatus - A List of CrawlerStatuses.
        latestProductsIngested - A List of the top N Products that have been ingested.
        jobHealthStatus - A List of JobHealthStatuses.
        crawlerHealthStatus - A List of CrawlerHealths.
